  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nWhen being on Import seed component, if I enter 1 word (or any number less than 12 / 18 / 24) - then the app is saying that entered seed is invalid.\r\nOn recent call with @xAlisher and @saledjenic and @glitchminer we discussed that could be changed the way when validation happens (trigger it after user enters his words). Just now this error message is a bit misleading because user has not finished his prompt yet, so nothing yet wrong has happened.\r\n\r\nChange it on the component level, so it applies everywhere\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-01-23 at 17 28 37\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/82375995/ecaddb3f-cfe9-469f-a1a4-f1703fbaa064\">\r\n",
